title: Danny & Josie Totah (Peacock's Saved by the Bell)
itunes:title: Danny & Josie Totah (Peacock's Saved by the Bell)
description:
Danny chats with actor Josie Totah who has a new podcast out called Dare We Say and also starred in the Saved by the Bell reboot, which was unjustly cancelled after 2 seasons. Josie tells us about her new show, working on Glee and what she hoped for in season 3 of SBTB.


BOOK: Smarturl.it/unremember
